# Keep `vercel --prod` uploads small (the app build doesn't need any of this).
# IMPORTANT: anchor dir names with a leading "/" so they match ONLY the repo
# root. A bare "worker" matches ANY dir named worker at any depth — it was
# silently excluding src/app/api/worker/ from the deploy, 404ing every
# /api/worker/* route in prod (pbdrain claim, result-ready, debug/cases, etc.)
# while they worked locally. Same trap for /docs.
/worker
/docs
*.csv
*.db
*.tsbuildinfo
Centner Labs
CSV Files
Chrome_Passwords.csv
claude
hard-reset.sh
